# Project Structure

```
src/
├── assets/           # CSS, fonts, images
├── data/
│   ├── constants/    # App-wide constants
│   ├── enums/        # App-wide enums
│   ├── hooks/        # React hooks
│   ├── providers/    # Data providers (API, JSON)
│   ├── services/     # HTTP client, utilities
│   ├── stores/       # Business logic (Model)
│   ├── types/        # Global TypeScript types
│   └── utils/        # Framework-agnostic utilities
├── views/
│   ├── components/   # Reusable UI components
│   ├── controllers/  # Shared ViewModels
│   └── pages/        # Page components with controllers
├── bindings.ts       # DI binding symbols
├── dependencies.ts   # DI container configuration
├── routes.tsx        # Application routes
└── index.tsx         # Application entry point
```

# Git Workflow

## Branches

- `main` / `master` - Production branch
- `uat` - Main development branch (auto-deploy)
- `preprod` - Pre-release branch for hot-fixes

## Commit Message Format

For Jira integration:

```
F2P1-XXXXX #time Xh description
```
